"{\"uid\": \"nytimes.com-athletic-5446454-2024-04-25-marta-brazil-olympics-retire\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Brazilian legendMartawill retire from international football this year.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 73, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 38-year-old confirmed the news in an interview with CNN Esportes S/A that airs Sunday, saying she is at peace with her decision given the promising future ofBrazil's national team, which has a pipeline of young, blossoming talent.\", \"from\": 75, \"to\": 309, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 131, \"end\": 134, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"score\": 0.9998330686978383, \"rank\": 0.0001669591147227346, \"text\": \"CNN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement  \\\"This is my last year, and I can already confirm it here.\", \"from\": 311, \"to\": 383, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is a moment when we have to understand that the time has come,\\\" Marta told CNN.\", \"from\": 384, \"to\": 469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 465, \"end\": 468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"score\": 0.9998330686978383, \"rank\": 0.0001669591147227346, \"text\": \"CNN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am very calm about this, because I see with great optimism this development that we are having in relation to young athletes.\\\"\", \"from\": 470, \"to\": 599, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Marta has appeared in fiveOlympicsthroughout her decorated career, winning silver medals in 2004 and 2008.\", \"from\": 603, \"to\": 709, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It remains to be seen if she will be chosen to represent Brazil at the Paris Olympics this summer but she said that, regardless, she will no longer be with the team come 2025.\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 885, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 767, \"end\": 773, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.826936325455527, \"rank\": 0.2092829395818563, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If I go to the Olympics, I will enjoy every moment, because regardless of whether I go to the Olympics or not, this is my last year with the national team,\\\" Martasaid to CNN.\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 1062, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1058, \"end\": 1061, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"score\": 0.9998330686978383, \"rank\": 0.0001669591147227346, \"text\": \"CNN\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CNN\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is no longer Marta in the national team as an athlete from 2025 onwards.\\\"\", \"from\": 1063, \"to\": 1143, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"GO DEEPER  Marta urges support for women's football after final World Cup elimination  Marta's impact on women's soccer has been paramount.\", \"from\": 1145, \"to\": 1284, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That much was evident after her emotional farewell from the World Cup stage last year.\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1372, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a tear-filled press conference that went viral, she told a room full of reporters: \\\"We ask the new generation to continue where we left off: continue to inspire even more girls and boys, no matter what age they are.\\\"\", \"from\": 1373, \"to\": 1592, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In January, she was presented with a FIFA Special Award \\\"following more than 20 years of stellar service to the sport\\\".\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1713, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She joined Canada'sChristine Sinclair, Portugal'sCristiano Ronaldoand fellow Brazilian Pele in receiving the honour.\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1830, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1725, \"end\": 1731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9999981535391947, \"rank\": 1.7751511008906567e-06, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marta has also been voted best player in the world six times between 2006 and 2018.\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1914, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Starting in 2025,FIFAalso said it will introduce the \\\"Marta Award\\\" for the best goal scored in women's football.\", \"from\": 1916, \"to\": 2028, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Though Marta says she will retire from international duty following the Olympics, she remains on contract with theOrlando Pridethrough the rest of the 2024 season.\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2193, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The team is undefeated and faces theWashington Spiritat Audi Field on Friday.\", \"from\": 2194, \"to\": 2271, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2250, \"end\": 2254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audi\", \"score\": 0.9995582270710474, \"rank\": 0.0002676047073745772, \"text\": \"Audi\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Audi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Ricardo Moreira/Getty Images)  Spot the pattern.\", \"from\": 2273, \"to\": 2322, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Connect the terms  Find the hidden link between sports terms  Play today's puzzle  Melanie Anzideiis a Staff Writer for The Athletic covering soccer.\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2472, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2406, \"end\": 2413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melanie_Griffith\", \"score\": 0.9987139994881699, \"rank\": 0.0012876148911972994, \"text\": \"Melanie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melanie_Griffith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melanie_Griffith\"}, {\"begin\": 2443, \"end\": 2455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Athletic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Athletic\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Athletic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Athletic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before joining The Athletic, she was an enterprise sports reporter for The Record newspaper and NorthJersey.com, where she was for nearly a decade.\", \"from\": 2473, \"to\": 2620, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2488, \"end\": 2500, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Athletic\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Athletic\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Athletic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Athletic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She's a graduate of Columbia Journalism School in New York City.Follow Melanie on Twitter@melanieanzidei\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2725, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2641, \"end\": 2667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Columbia_University_Graduate_School_of_Journalism\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Columbia Journalism School\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Columbia_University_Graduate_School_of_Journalism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Columbia_University_Graduate_School_of_Journalism\"}, {\"begin\": 2671, \"end\": 2679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999923853528131, \"rank\": 7.524723024053379e-06, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 2692, \"end\": 2699, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melanie_Griffith\", \"score\": 0.9987139994881699, \"rank\": 0.0012876148911972994, \"text\": \"Melanie\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melanie_Griffith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Melanie_Griffith\"}]}]}"